'''天主教清邁教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Chiangmaiensis}}；{{lang-th|สังฆมณฑลเชียงใหม่}}）是[[泰國|泰國]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教曼谷總教區|曼谷總教區]]。

1959年11月17日設[[監牧|監牧區]]，1965年12月18日升為教區。<ref>{{cite web |title=DE THAILANDIA |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19651218_de-thailandia.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-07-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190724191326/https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19651218_de-thailandia.html |archivedate=2019-07-24 |language=la |date=1965-12-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2018年4月25日[[天主教清萊教區|清萊教區]]析出。<ref name="Vatican20180425">{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 25.04.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2018/04/25/0299/00649.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190724162542/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2018/04/25/0299/00649.html |archivedate=2019-07-24 |language=it |date=2018-04-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

教區範圍包括[[泰北地區|泰北地區]]的五個府：[[清邁府|清邁府]]、[[南奔府|南奔府]]、除敖縣以外的[[南邦府|南邦府]]、[[帕府|帕府]]和[[夜豐頌府|夜豐頌府]]。2018年有教友50,913人、三十一個堂區、四十七名司鐸。<ref name="Vatican20180425" />現任教區主教為{{link-en|方濟各·沙勿略·威叻·阿蓬拉達那|Francis Xavier Vira Arpondratana}}，榮休主教為{{link-de|若瑟·桑萬·素拉沙朗|Joseph Sangval Surasarang}}。<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 10.02.2009 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/02/10/0098/00240.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190724170502/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/02/10/0098/00240.html |archivedate=2019-07-24 |language=it |date=2009-02-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

